## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies or the latest developments in social engineering defense. Additionally, the effectiveness of these practices can vary depending on the specific context and environment of an organization. Continuous updates and adaptations of these strategies are recommended to address evolving threats.